# Autogolpe environment variables.
#
# Preferred: secrets live OUTSIDE this repo at ~/.local/share/secrets/autogolpe.env (mode 600).
# direnv (.envrc, committed) loads them automatically when you cd into this directory.
#   1. mkdir -p ~/.local/share/secrets && chmod 700 ~/.local/share/secrets
#   2. cp .env.example ~/.local/share/secrets/autogolpe.env
#   3. Fill in real values in ~/.local/share/secrets/autogolpe.env
#   4. chmod 600 ~/.local/share/secrets/autogolpe.env
#   5. direnv allow .
#
# Docker note: docker-compose.yml has `env_file: .env`. A symlink at ./.env -> the
# secrets file lets compose pick up the same values without duplicating. Create with:
#   ln -s ~/.local/share/secrets/autogolpe.env .env
# The symlink target is gitignored; the symlink itself is gitignored via the existing .env rule.
#
# Variables:

BSKY_SERVICE=
BSKY_IDENTIFIER=
BSKY_PASSWORD=
DB_PATH=
LIVE_DMS=
